raw_text = "~ start
Mom: Hey honey! How are you settling in?
PlayerM: Moooom 🥺
Mom: Yes sweeetie
PlayerM: Mom I miss youu already
PlayerM: I miss Ms Whiskers and my bed
PlayerM: img: mabel/9
Mom: I miss you too 🥰
Mom: You can do it honey, hang in there
Mom: It's only your first day
Mom: I'm sure you'll make a lot of friends and have a good time soon enough
PlayerM: I can't, I wanna come home 😭
Mom: I'd love nothing more to hug my big girl but life is life honey 🥹
Mom: Don't grow up too fast
Mom: Doesn't your boyfriend go there too now?
PlayerM: He does 😊
PlayerM: He's the best!
Mom: There you go! You're in good hands
Mom: Say hi to him for me
Mom: And make sure to study hard
PlayerM: I will mom
Mom: And eat well okay? No more late night snacking!
PlayerM: Okay, I promise I won't
Mom: But if the cafeteria food isn't good then I packed you a box of a few meals that should be good for this month
PlayerM: Omg thanks Mom, you're the bestest
PlayerM: That makes me miss you even more omg
Mom: Love you baby, it's getting late
Mom: Make sure you don't ruin your sleep okay?
PlayerM: Okay, good night mom
Mom: Good night baby ❤️
=> END"
